{"tid":183901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【警方偵破會員制援交網站拘23人，年紀最輕的只有17歲。】","createTime":"2017-04-02T12:35:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T02:35:57.000Z","uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"893389265f057613089d5b6ee66a213bf7aa3d4f","tid":183901,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:35:26.000Z","msg":"警方打擊援交網站，拘捕23人。網站運作五年，會員人數達十萬，收益超過二千萬。警方指集團透過「會員分級制」及「助養計劃」，要求男士繳交會費及每月供款，以瀏覽女會員資料及進行性交易。被捕人士除了網站骨幹成員、嫖客，亦有涉嫌援交的女子，年紀最輕的只有17歲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/652359628289442/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F652359628289442%2F&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=2f7709a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/652359628289442/</a><br />\n<br />\n#有線電視 #援交"},{"pid":"c6decb30961a4107b3e46e666143fc74666a7aaa","tid":183901,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:36:05.000Z","msg":"助養計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d07943e8c6da26dc9b32b6a728cfb211ef2ccb81","tid":183901,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T02:35:57.000Z","msg":"有冇所有囡囡嘅打包zip檔<br />\n想睇吓身邊有冇兄弟個老婆之前出嚟做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明上次大人網都有囡囡資料流出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <a href=\"http://forum4.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=BW&amp;message=6250769\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum4.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DBW%26message%3D6250769&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=eb225136\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum4.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=BW&amp;message=6250769</a>"}]}